expanded.description: If true, expands any nested navigation in the item, otherwise collapse it.

href.description: Link href for when the item is rendered as a link.

id.description: A string that uniquely identifies the item.

isSidebarFullyCollapsed.description: If true, the containing sidebar is fully collapsed.

isSidebarFullyExpanded.description: If true, the containing sidebar is fully expanded.

Link.description: The component used to render the item as a link.

mini.description: If true, the containing sidebar is in mini mode.

onClick.description: Callback fired when the item is clicked.

renderNestedNavigation.description: Override the component rendered as nested navigation for this item.
